# Cloudflare Pages redirects/rewrites.
# -------------------------------------
# Serve the bare /favicon.ico convention path (requested by bots, crawlers and
# legacy clients regardless of the declared PNG/SVG icons) from our existing
# 32x32 icon. A 200 rewrite returns the asset in place — no extra binary file,
# single source of truth — and removes a recurring 404 from the error rate.
/favicon.ico  /favicon-32x32.png  200
